  "detailed_description": "Altered is a meditative puzzle game mixing hard puzzles and a soothing atmosphere.<br>Explore a mysterious world filled with challenging puzzles solving them by altering your characters in multiple ways, forcing you to think outside the box.<br>Take your time and solve at your own pace, as you make your way through.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/99a79c24c43bca0f869e68c42b99fee1.poster.avif?t=1674461633\" width=416 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/99a79c24c43bca0f869e68c42b99fee1.webm?t=1674461633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/99a79c24c43bca0f869e68c42b99fee1.mp4?t=1674461633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>Challenge yourself by solving one of over 80 puzzles, with the twist of altering each character using their unique powers.<br>By understanding their powers, you will gain new intuition for solving interesting puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/763d67c72a536bfaf76dd9e6577f5510.poster.avif?t=1674461633\" width=416 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/763d67c72a536bfaf76dd9e6577f5510.webm?t=1674461633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/763d67c72a536bfaf76dd9e6577f5510.mp4?t=1674461633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973250/extras/ac8158693cccf95fb0d2c17ff6ade295.avif?t=1674461633\" width=275 height=138 /></span><br>Altered was selected to the  Copenhagen Game Collective Yonderplay Showcase at the 2019 Nordic Game Conference.",
